{"tid":1238450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信sd比班議員，希望可以代為追查各個嚴重受傷義士情況！！！","createTime":"2019-06-17T23:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:24:56.000Z","uid":34816,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee45f2688a6455e99db6bbc078d97ed5931240c3","tid":1238450,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:28:58.000Z","msg":"痴線就黎成個星期，三個嚴重受傷義士(頭部中彈，港台司機，口鼻出血)既確實消息可以係完全唔見，好難想像呢種情況會係香港發生。<br />\n<br />\n究竟係咪有港府高層蓄意隱瞞！？我地一定要查清查楚！可能我地權限唔夠接觸唔到&ldquo;敏感&rdquo;資料，但相信班議員絕對有能力搞清楚成個情況，我地唔可以比件事就咁消音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懇請大家一齊send 信比鄺仔朱凱迪等一眾議員，比壓力佢地去主動徹查事件！"},{"pid":"4a74607325a909bf24eee07d1cb41b135dfd52a2","tid":1238450,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:31:54.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"aa174ac2a3d51a897713096c6e6dd26b7a9d5236","tid":1238450,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26117fe83cb874fc8ed904aa2984b4b3efa89fc9","tid":1238450,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfebb2adbd720b159d9bdf0f1852100eef5a0349","tid":1238450,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:37:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7b4cd1b2b4c54c678ba64c92d769788bd7a75d2","tid":1238450,"uid":45188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcc887c58f6049951652f34f8b62c8186a3b7d2f","tid":1238450,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:44:09.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推！"},{"pid":"d2d3cc5ee5400930da69d94623fb14c2440a9ed6","tid":1238450,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb071584a40e1149026ad3997992adcb3d6bc542","tid":1238450,"uid":197110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06